BTTAdditionalActions.BTTInlineAppleScript: tell application "System Preferences"	activate	set the current pane to pane id "com.apple.preference.network"	return get the name of every anchor of pane id "com.apple.preference.network"	reveal anchor "Wi-Fi" of pane id "com.apple.preference.network"end tell
